name: COCKER
description: Cocker Token; is a decentralized DeFi project that brings together the pet and crypto market under a common roof. Aiming to unite the petshop world, which has a 150 billion dollar market in the world, with cryptocurrencies, CockerToken aims to structure the petshop world we are accustomed to on the online platform and to establish an interactive ecosystem circulating between the buyer-seller-investor under the name of Cocker Market.
